-1.0                    charge
1.0                     mass        Species 1: H+
1.0                     charge
16.0                    mass        Species 2: O+
1.0                     charge
32.0                    mass        Species 3: O2+
1.0                     charge
44.0                    mass        Species 4: CO2+
1.0                     charge

